Prince Harry and Meghan Markle could find themselves facing a fresh wave of revelations when Sarah Ferguson releases her own tell-all book. The publication, titled "A Most Intriguing Lady", will see the former wife of Prince Andrew "talking about her relationship with the Queen and answer a few questions about Harry and Meghan". The Duchess of York is also set to host an event to promote the book. Its release will come weeks after a host of bombshell claims against the Royal Family from Harry and Meghan, with the couple starring in their own six-part documentary series and the prince releasing his memoir, Spare. FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES: